Mountain lion known as P-22 was found in the crawl space of a Los Feliz home on Monday . 
  California Department of Fish and Wildlife said the cougar has 'left the building' and is heading back to Griffith Park . 
  He was discovered in the home by an alarm technician at midday on Monday  . 
  Animal services tried to move the lion - firing tennis balls and using a camera - but he refused to leave . 
  The cougar was spotted in front of the Hollywood sign in 2013  . 
 